#: C/shell-overview.page:28(page/title)
msgid "Desktop, apps &amp; windows"
msgstr "桌面、應用程式與視窗"

#: C/shell-overview.page:33(section/title)
msgid "The Desktop"
msgstr "桌面"

#: C/shell-overview.page:37(section/title)
msgid "Applications and windows"
msgstr "應用程式與視窗"

#: C/shell-overview.page:41(section/title)
msgid "Add and remove software"
msgstr "加入和移除軟體"

#: C/shell-windows-maximize.page:10(info/desc)
msgid "Double-click or drag a titlebar to maximize or restore a window."
msgstr "雙擊或拖曳標題列，可以最大化或還原視窗。"

#: C/shell-windows-maximize.page:23(page/title)
msgid "Maximize and unmaximize a window"
msgstr "最大化和取消最大化視窗"

#: C/shell-windows-maximize.page:25(page/p)
msgid ""
"You can maximize a window to take up all of the space on your desktop and "
"unmaximize a window to restore it to its normal size. You can also maximize "
"windows vertically along the left and right sides of the screen, so you can "
"easily look at two windows at once. See <link xref=\"shell-windows-tiled\"/> "
"for details."
msgstr ""
"您可以將視窗最大化，填滿您桌面的所有空間，將可以取消視窗的最大化，將它還原成正常大小。您也可以將視窗沿著螢幕左/右側垂直最大化，讓您可以輕易地一次檢視兩個"
"視窗。詳情請參閱<link xref=\"shell-windows-tiled\"/>。"

#: C/shell-windows-maximize.page:31(page/p)
msgid ""
"To maximize a window, grab the titlebar and drag it to the top of the "
"screen, or just double-click the titlebar. To maximize a window using the "
"keyboard, hold down the <link xref=\"windows-key\">windows key</link> and "
"press <key>↑</key>."
msgstr ""
"若要最大化視窗，抓住標題列並將它拖曳至螢幕頂端，或是直接在標題列上雙擊。若要用鍵盤最大化視窗，按住 <link xref=\"windows-"
"key\">Windows 鍵</link> 並按 <key>↑</key>。"

#: C/shell-windows-maximize.page:36(page/p)
msgid ""
"To restore a window to its unmaximized size, drag it away from the edges of "
"the screen. If the window is fully maximized, you can double-click the "
"titlebar to restore it. You can also use the keyboard shortcut <link "
"xref=\"windows-key\">windows key</link> and <key>↓</key>."
msgstr ""
"若要將視窗還原成未最大化的大小，將它拖離螢幕邊緣。如果視窗已經完全最大化，您可以雙擊標題列來還原它。您也可以使用鍵盤捷徑鍵：<link "
"xref=\"windows-key\">Windows 鍵</link> + <key>↓</key>。"

#: C/shell-windows-maximize.page:42(note/p)
#: C/shell-windows-tiled.page:38(note/p)
msgid ""
"Hold down the <key>Alt</key> key and drag anywhere in a window to move it."
msgstr "按住 <key>Alt</key> 鍵，拖曳視窗內任何一處來移動視窗。"

#: C/shell-windows.page:9(info/desc)
msgid "Move and organize your windows."
msgstr "移動並組織您的視窗。"

#: C/shell-windows.page:22(page/title)
msgid "Windows and workspaces"
msgstr "視窗與工作區"

#: C/shell-windows.page:24(page/p)
msgid ""
"Like other desktops, Unity uses windows to display your running "
"applications. Using both the <gui>dash</gui> and the <gui>launcher</gui>, "
"you can launch new applications and control which window is active."
msgstr ""
"就跟其他桌面環境一樣，Unity 用視窗來顯示正在執行的應用程式。只要用 <gui>Dash</gui> "
"以及<gui>啟動器</gui>，您便可以啟動新的應用程式，並控制要以哪個視窗為活動視窗。"

#: C/shell-windows.page:26(page/p)
msgid ""
"In addition to windows, you can also group your applications together within "
"workspaces. Visit the window and workspace help topics below to better learn "
"how to use these features."
msgstr "除了視窗，您也可以利用工作區，將應用程式給組織起來。想要多了解這些功能的使用方式嗎？就請閱覽「視窗與工作區」的以下幫助主題吧。"

#: C/shell-windows.page:50(info/title)
msgctxt "link:trail"
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "視窗"

#: C/shell-windows.page:52(section/title)
msgid "Working with windows"
msgstr "以視窗進行工作"

#: C/shell-windows.page:57(info/title)
msgctxt "link:trail"
msgid "Workspaces"
msgstr "工作區"

#: C/shell-windows.page:59(section/title)
msgid "Working with workspaces"
msgstr "以工作區進行工作"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:9(info/desc)
msgid "Restore, resize, arrange and hide."
msgstr "還原、調整大小、整理和隱藏。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:22(page/title)
msgid "Window operations"
msgstr "視窗操作"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:29(page/p)
msgid "Windows can be resized or concealed to suit workflow."
msgstr "您可以調整視窗的大小或隱藏視窗，以配合您的工作計畫。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:37(section/title)
msgid "Minimize, restore and close"
msgstr "最小化、還原與關閉"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:39(section/p)
msgid "To minimize or hide a window:"
msgstr "若要最小化或隱藏視窗："

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:42(item/p)
msgid ""
"Click the <gui>-</gui> in the top left hand corner of the application's "
"<gui>menu bar</gui>. If the application is maximized (taking up your whole "
"screen), the menu bar will appear at the very top of the screen. Otherwise, "
"the minimize button will appear at the top of the application window."
msgstr ""
"點擊應用程式<gui>選單列</gui>左上角的 <gui>-</gui> "
"圖示。如果程式已被最大化（佔用了您全部的螢幕），選單列會出現在螢幕的最頂端；若否，則最小化按鈕會出現在程式視窗的頂端處。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:47(item/p)
msgid ""
"Or press <keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>Space</key></keyseq> to bring up the "
"window menu. Then press <key>n</key>. The window 'disappears' into the "
"launcher."
msgstr ""
"或是按 <keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>空白鍵</key></keyseq> 叫出視窗選單。接著按 "
"<key>n</key>。視窗就會「消失」，回到啟動器。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:53(section/p)
msgid "To restore the window:"
msgstr "若要還原視窗："

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:56(item/p)
msgid ""
"Click on it in the <link xref=\"unity-launcher-intro\">launcher</link> or "
"retrieve it from the window switcher by pressing "
"<keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>Tab</key></keyseq>."
msgstr ""
"點擊<link xref=\"unity-launcher-intro\">啟動器</link>上的程式位置，或是按 "
"<keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>Tab</key></keyseq>，從視窗切換器將它叫回。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:62(section/p)
msgid "To close the window:"
msgstr "若要關閉視窗："

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:65(item/p)
msgid "Click the <gui>x</gui> in the top left hand corner of the window, or"
msgstr "點擊視窗左上角的 <gui>x</gui>，或者"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:68(item/p)
msgid "Press <keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>F4</key></keyseq>, or"
msgstr "按 <keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>F4</key></keyseq>，或者"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:71(item/p)
msgid ""
"Press <keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>Space</key></keyseq> to bring up the window "
"menu. Then press <key>c</key>."
msgstr ""
"按 <keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>空白鍵</key></keyseq>叫出視窗選單。接著按下 <key>c</key>。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:79(section/title)
msgid "Resize"
msgstr "調整大小"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:82(note/p)
msgid "A window cannot be resized if it is <em>maximized</em>."
msgstr "<em>最大化</em>的視窗，大小是無法調整的。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:84(section/p)
msgid "To resize your window horizontally and/or vertically:"
msgstr "若要調整您的視窗水平、垂直大小："

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:87(item/p)
msgid ""
"Move the mouse pointer into any corner of the window until it changes into a "
"'corner-pointer'. Click+hold+drag to resize the window in any direction."
msgstr "移動滑鼠游標至視窗的任何角落，直到游標變成「角落加游標」為止。點擊、按穩後拖曳，就能以任意方向改變視窗的大小。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:91(section/p)
msgid "To resize only in the horizontal direction:"
msgstr "若只要調整水平方向的大小："

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:94(item/p)
msgid ""
"Move the mouse pointer to either side of the window until it changes into a "
"'side-pointer'. Click+hold+drag to resize the window horizontally."
msgstr "移動滑鼠游標至視窗任兩側，直到游標變成「邊加游標」為止。點擊、按穩後拖曳，就能以水平方向改變視窗的大小。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:98(section/p)
msgid "To resize only in the vertical direction:"
msgstr "若只要調整垂直方向的大小："

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:101(item/p)
msgid ""
"Move the mouse pointer to the top or bottom of the window until it changes "
"into a 'top-pointer' or 'bottom-pointer' respectively. Click+hold+drag to "
"resize the window vertically."
msgstr "移動滑鼠游標至視窗頂端或底端，直到游標變成「頂加游標」或「底加游標」為止。點擊、按穩後拖曳，就能以垂直方向改變視窗的大小。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:111(section/title)
msgid "Arranging windows in your workspace"
msgstr "在您的工作區組織視窗"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:113(section/p)
msgid "To place two windows side by side:"
msgstr "若要將兩個視窗邊對邊對齊："

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:116(item/p)
msgid ""
"Click on the <gui>title bar</gui> of a window and drag it toward the left "
"edge of the screen. When the <gui>mouse pointer</gui> touches the edge, the "
"left half of the screen becomes highlighted. Release the mouse button and "
"the window will fill the left half of the screen."
msgstr ""
"點擊其中一個視窗的<gui>標題列</gui>，將它拖曳至螢幕左邊緣。當<gui>滑鼠游標</gui>碰到邊緣時，螢幕的左半邊會被標亮。放開滑鼠按鈕，視窗"
"將會填滿左半邊螢幕。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:120(item/p)
msgid ""
"Drag another window to the right side: when the right half of the screen is "
"highlighted, release. Each of the two windows fills half the screen."
msgstr "將另外一個視窗拖向右側：當右半邊的螢幕被標亮時放開按鍵。這兩個視窗將各填滿半個螢幕。"

#: C/shell-windows-states.page:126(note/p)
msgid ""
"Pressing <key>Alt</key> + click anywhere in a window will allow you to move "
"the window. Some people may find this easier than clicking on the <gui>title "
"bar</gui> of an application."
msgstr ""
"按 <key>Alt</key> 並點擊視窗內任何一處，就可以移動視窗。對某些人而言，這會比點擊應用程式的<gui>標題列</gui>容易。."

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:11(info/desc)
msgid "Press <keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>Tab</key></keyseq>."
msgstr "按下 <keyseq><key>Alt</key><key>Tab</key></keyseq>。"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:26(page/title)
msgid "Switch between windows"
msgstr "在視窗間切換"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:34(section/title)
msgid "From the launcher"
msgstr "用啟動器"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:36(item/p)
msgid ""
"Show the <gui>launcher</gui> by moving your mouse to the top left corner of "
"your screen."
msgstr "將您的滑鼠移動至螢幕左上角，顯示<gui>啟動器</gui>。"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:39(item/p)
msgid ""
"Applications that are running have a small white triangle arrow on the left. "
"Click on a running application icon to switch to it."
msgstr "若有任何應用程式在執行，圖示的左邊會有一個小小的白色三角形箭頭。點擊任何一個執行中程式即可切換。"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:43(item/p)
msgid ""
"If a running application has multiple windows open, there will be multiple "
"white arrows on the left. Click the application icon a second time to show "
"all open windows zoomed out. Click the window you want to switch to."
msgstr "如果執行中的程式開啟了數個視窗，圖示左邊會有數個白色箭頭。點擊該程式圖示第二次，會以縮圖的方式顯示所有開啟的視窗。點擊您要切換至的視窗。"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:52(section/title)
msgid "From the keyboard"
msgstr "用鍵盤"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:56(item/p)
msgid ""
"When you hold down the <key>Alt</key> key and then press <key>Tab</key>, a "
"<em>window switcher</em> appears. This shows a list of the windows you have "
"open, with a preview."
msgstr ""
"當您按住 <key>Alt</key> 鍵不放並按下 "
"<key>Tab</key>，會出現一個<em>視窗切換器</em>。它列出了您開啟的所有視窗，並附上預覽。"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:61(item/p)
msgid ""
"You can continue pressing <key>Tab</key> as many times as you need to reach "
"the window you want."
msgstr "您可以繼續按 <key>Tab</key> 好幾次，以便到您要的視窗去。"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:64(item/p)
msgid ""
"To switch to the previous window, hold down the <key>Alt</key> key and press "
"<keyseq><key>Shift</key><key>Tab</key></keyseq> instead."
msgstr ""
"若要切換至前一個視窗，按住 <key>Alt</key> 鍵不放並按下 "
"<keyseq><key>Shift</key><key>Tab</key></keyseq>。"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:68(item/p)
msgid ""
"Only windows from the current <link xref=\"shell-"
"workspaces\">workspace</link> will be shown. To show windows from all "
"workspaces, hold down the <key>Ctrl</key> and <key>Alt</key> keys and press "
"<key>Tab</key> or <keyseq><key>Shift</key><key>Tab</key></keyseq>."
msgstr ""
"只有目前<link xref=\"shell-workspaces\">工作區</link>下的視窗會被顯示。若要顯示所有工作區的視窗，按住 "
"<key>Ctrl</key> 和 <key>Alt</key> 鍵不放，並按 <key>Tab</key> 或是 "
"<keyseq><key>Shift</key><key>Tab</key></keyseq>。"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:77(item/p)
msgid ""
"Press <keyseq><key>Windows</key><key>W</key></keyseq> to show all open "
"windows zoomed out."
msgstr "按下 <keyseq><key>Windows</key><key>W</key></keyseq>，以縮圖方式顯示所有開啟的視窗。"

#: C/shell-windows-switching.page:81(item/p)
msgid "Click the window you want to switch to."
msgstr "點擊您要切換至的視窗。"

#: C/shell-windows-tiled.page:10(info/desc)
msgid "Maximize two windows side-by-side."
msgstr "將兩個視窗最大化、邊對邊對齊。"

#: C/shell-windows-tiled.page:23(page/title)
msgid "Tile windows"
msgstr "平鋪視窗"

#: C/shell-windows-tiled.page:25(page/p)
msgid ""
"You can maximize a window on only the left or right side of the screen, "
"allowing you to place two windows side-by-side to quickly switch between "
"them."
msgstr "您可以讓視窗只最大化到螢幕左側或右側，這樣您就可以放兩個邊對邊的視窗，在它們之間快速切換。"

#: C/shell-windows-tiled.page:29(page/p)
msgid ""
"To maximize a window along a side of the screen, grab the titlebar and drag "
"it to the left or right side until half of the screen is highlighted. Using "
"the keyboard, hold down the <link xref=\"windows-key\">windows key</link> "
"and press the <key>Left</key> or <key>Right</key> key."
msgstr ""
"若要讓視窗沿著螢幕的某一側最大化，抓住標題列後，將它拖曳至左側或右側，直到半邊的螢幕被標亮。用鍵盤的話，按住 <link xref=\"windows-"
"key\">Windows 鍵</link>不放，並按<key>左方向鍵</key>或<key>右方向鍵</key>。"

#: C/shell-windows-tiled.page:34(page/p)
msgid ""
"To restore a window to its original size, drag it away from the side of the "
"screen, or use the same keyboard shortcut you used to maximize."
msgstr "若要將視窗恢復成原本的大小，就將它拖離螢幕側邊，或是用您剛剛用來最大化的同一個鍵盤快捷鍵。"

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:11(info/desc)
msgid ""
"Open the workspace switcher and drag the window to a different workspace."
msgstr "開啟工作區切換器，並拖曳視窗到不同的工作區。"

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:26(page/title)
msgid "Move a window to a different workspace"
msgstr "移動視窗到不同的工作區"

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:28(page/p)
#: C/shell-workspaces-switch.page:29(item/title)
msgid "Using the mouse:"
msgstr "使用滑鼠："

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:32(item/p)
msgid ""
"Open the <link xref=\"unity-launcher-intro\">Launcher</link> and click the "
"<gui>workspace switcher</gui> button near the bottom."
msgstr ""
"打開<link xref=\"unity-launcher-intro\">啟動器</link>並點擊靠近底部的<gui>工作區切換器</gui>。"

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:36(item/p)
msgid "Drag the window to the workspace you choose."
msgstr "將視窗拖曳至您選擇的工作區。"

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:40(page/p)
#: C/shell-workspaces-switch.page:34(item/title)
msgid "Using the keyboard:"
msgstr "使用鍵盤："

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:43(item/p)
msgid "Select the window you want to move."
msgstr "選擇您要移動的視窗。"

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:46(item/p)
msgid ""
"Press "
"<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Alt</key><key>Shift</key><key>→</key></keyseq> "
"to move the window to a workspace which is to the right of the current "
"workspace on the <gui>workspace switcher</gui>."
msgstr ""
"按 "
"<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Alt</key><key>Shift</key><key>→</key></keyseq>，讓視"
"窗移動至<gui>工作區切換器</gui>中目前工作區右邊的工作區。"

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:52(item/p)
msgid ""
"Press "
"<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Alt</key><key>Shift</key><key>←</key></keyseq> "
"to move the window to a workspace which is to the left of the current "
"workspace on the <gui>workspace switcher</gui>."
msgstr ""
"按 "
"<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Alt</key><key>Shift</key><key>←</key></keyseq>，讓視"
"窗移動至<gui>工作區切換器</gui>中目前工作區左邊的工作區。"

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:58(item/p)
msgid ""
"Press "
"<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Alt</key><key>Shift</key><key>↓</key></keyseq> "
"to move the window to a workspace which is below the current workspace on "
"the <gui>workspace switcher</gui>."
msgstr ""
"按 "
"<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Alt</key><key>Shift</key><key>↓</key></keyseq>，讓視"
"窗移動至<gui>工作區切換器</gui>中目前工作區下面的工作區。"

#: C/shell-workspaces-movewindow.page:64(item/p)
msgid ""
"Press "
"<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Alt</key><key>Shift</key><key>↑</key></keyseq> "
"to move the window to a workspace which is above the current workspace on "
"the <gui>workspace switcher</gui>."
msgstr ""
"按 "
"<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>Alt</key><key>Shift</key><key>↑</key></keyseq>，讓視"
"窗移動至<gui>工作區切換器</gui>中目前工作區上面的工作區。"

