msgstr "存取目前的時間與日期。"

#: C/unity-appmenu-intro.page:60(item/p)
msgid ""
"<em>User menu</em> <media type=\"image\" mime=\"image/svg\" "
"src=\"/usr/share/icons/ubuntu-mono-light/stock/22/stock_person-"
"panel.svg\">User offline icon</media>"
